          </infoLinks>
          <rules>
            <rule name="Indynabula Array" id="bee8-56a7-816a-0d2f" hidden="false">
              <description>The array allows Valthex to attempt to repair a vehicle as if he were equipped with a Servo-Arm. In addition, it counts as 2 Power Weapons (extra attack included in profile). It also confers a 5+ invulnerable save.</description>
            </rule>
            <rule name="Battle Alchemistry" id="755a-ba82-0b6d-8ed2" hidden="false">
              <description>An army including Valthrex can upgrade a single Space Marine unit within the army as having Hellfire Rounds equipped in any Bolt Pistol, Bolter or Storm Bolter. Hellfire rounds as per the weapon they are equipped with, but wound any target on a 2+.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
