          <rules>
            <rule name="Rage unto Death" id="2086-0bd8-ab37-a287" hidden="false">
              <description>Once Phoros has lost one or more wounds he gains +1 Strength and +1 Attack. In addition, once he has lost one or more wounds he must attempt to charge whenever possible and must always sweeping advance and consolidate toward the nearest enemy models within Line of Sight.</description>
            </rule>
            <rule name="Lord of Ruin" id="935e-e314-97ae-466a" hidden="false">
              <description>Any Lamenters unit Phoros joins automatically pass any Pinning or Morale checks they are required to take. Any enemy units that lose a combat that involves Phoros must re-roll successful Morale checks.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
