            <rule name="Firefall" id="9058-fc64-9337-aff1" hidden="false">
              <description>If the mission has the Deep Strike special rule then Courbray and any squad he has joined must start the game in reserve. When they arrive from Deep Strike, after scatter has been resolved, every unit (friend or foe) within 6&quot; of Courbray or his squad recieves D6 S4 AP5 hits as if from shooting. In addition, Courbray and his unit count as having a cover save of 5+ until the start of their next player turn.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
