          </infoLinks>
          <rules>
            <rule name="Actinic Halo" id="66bf-a17c-1cf0-aabe" hidden="false">
              <description>Provides a 3+ invulnerable save. However, should this be failed and Narvaez survive, roll a D6. On a 1-3 the Halo stops functioning, on a 4+ it continues to work as usual.</description>
            </rule>
            <rule name="Dark Void Elite" id="c7f7-50a9-a1de-b7c3" hidden="false">
              <description>When Narvaez is included in an army, one Tactical Squad may be chosen to represent veterans of the Chapter&apos;s long voyages into the outer-galactic darkness. Both Narvaez and this chosen squad have the Infiltrator and Move Through Cover veteran skills.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
        </selectionEntry>
