            <rule name="Terminator Attack" id="b471-e917-09f9-3ce8" hidden="false">
              <description>When an army includes Mordaci, any Terminator, Terminator Assault and Terminator Command Squads that are held in Reserve to Deep Strike may re-roll 1&apos;s for their Reserve Rolls, and can choose to re-roll their Deep Strike scatter.</description>
