        <infoLink name="Purity Seals" id="2980-bd77-f34b-5aac" hidden="false" type="rule" targetId="8fca-253c-bbf8-9510"/>
      </infoLinks>
      <rules>
        <rule name="The Hellslayer" id="799b-a860-662d-b9fc" hidden="false">
          <description>The Hellslayer is a massive barbed and sigil-etched power mace that is a deadly bane to the witch and the daemon. The Hellslayer counts as a Master-crafted Thunder Hammer, but requires two hands to use (Alberec cannot claim an extra attack from having a pistol). In addition to the Thunder Hammer abilitys (Strikes Last; Shaken Results on hit vehicles; Prevents attacks by models wounded), it also has the following; Against targets which are either daemons or that know psychic powers of any kind, all successful to hit rolls wound automatically.</description>
        </rule>
        <rule name="Soul Seared" id="abfe-10f0-a7cf-7e67" hidden="false">
          <description>Whenever Alberec is targeted by a psychic power, including any squad he is joined, or vehicle he is mounted in, roll a D6. On a 4+ the power is nullified and nothing happens.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
    </selectionEntry>
